  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're an amateur or a professional FPV pilot, improve your skills or start fresh with <strong>Drones of War</strong>! With its realistic simulation based on real flight dynamics, customize your own FPV drone and feel like you're flying in a real battlefield—without risking your drone! Explore diverse maps and strengthen your knowledge and experience by battling against AI-controlled enemies. Hone your piloting skills in high-stakes scenarios, strategize your attacks, and master the art of precision strikes in this intense FPV kamikaze simulator. Test your limits, dominate the battlefield, and take your FPV gameplay to the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't have a drone controller yet: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                                    MAPS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beach</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rural</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/90d6290c5bf78fd502ef01df0a4eabed.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/90d6290c5bf78fd502ef01df0a4eabed.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/90d6290c5bf78fd502ef01df0a4eabed.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pole</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/ad576b74867c5dd2e5a19ea985dbe46f.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/ad576b74867c5dd2e5a19ea985dbe46f.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/ad576b74867c5dd2e5a19ea985dbe46f.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acro Area</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/60dbeba285d718a17773a95a749c7586.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/60dbeba285d718a17773a95a749c7586.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/60dbeba285d718a17773a95a749c7586.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ruined City</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/a4c8008e260648712dd0972f872148c0.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/a4c8008e260648712dd0972f872148c0.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/a4c8008e260648712dd0972f872148c0.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                                          <strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thermal</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can easily locate enemies with a thermal camera, but you need to choose your controller wisely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/01ae415492644997152e41bb04c93b8b.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/01ae415492644997152e41bb04c93b8b.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/01ae415492644997152e41bb04c93b8b.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wind</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid the winds in different areas of the maps; otherwise, you may lose balance!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/1874b5fd1c426c04d2d9f535d2f0bc93.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/1874b5fd1c426c04d2d9f535d2f0bc93.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/1874b5fd1c426c04d2d9f535d2f0bc93.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jammer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay away from jammers in different areas of the maps; otherwise, your movements may be restricted!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/95669411c9b3b127c27ff53fe9561aa2.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/95669411c9b3b127c27ff53fe9561aa2.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/95669411c9b3b127c27ff53fe9561aa2.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lock-on Card</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you activate the lock-on card, you can perform a two-stage lock-on. The first stage requires you to control the throttle. The second stage is the easiest—just lock on, and the drone will go!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/aa0cf85a5ff4911aa588f07fbb6e693c.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/aa0cf85a5ff4911aa588f07fbb6e693c.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/aa0cf85a5ff4911aa588f07fbb6e693c.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're an amateur or a professional FPV pilot, improve your skills or start fresh with <strong>Drones of War</strong>! With its realistic simulation based on real flight dynamics, customize your own FPV drone and feel like you're flying in a real battlefield—without risking your drone! Explore diverse maps and strengthen your knowledge and experience by battling against AI-controlled enemies. Hone your piloting skills in high-stakes scenarios, strategize your attacks, and master the art of precision strikes in this intense FPV kamikaze simulator. Test your limits, dominate the battlefield, and take your FPV gameplay to the next level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you don't have a drone controller yet: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>                                                                    MAPS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beach</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=690 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.webm?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/2e4900fa27f18157fd9df2f8ae90a2ba.mp4?t=1774268860\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rural</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3484690/extras/90d6290c5bf78fd502ef01df0a4eabed.poster.avif?t=1774268860\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/